Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/L%C3%A2m-chung-di-ch%C3%BAc/poem-QFH-wPiNVjHgLSWJ0BGSfg">Lâm chung di chúc - 臨終遺囑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-B3gaZnYZj3Y7n162MsC6mQ">Trần Quốc Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/L%E1%BB%99-qu%C3%A1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-H%E1%BA%A3i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-ng%C5%A9-c%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-kzcEQT3mDPWAo5nViNxK_A">Lộ quá Bắc Ninh, Hải Dương tức sự hữu cảm ngũ cổ thập lục vận - 路過北寧海陽即事有感五古十六韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/T%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-MaEHcbrNq5WrmoolmBF7hw">Tân đình ngẫu đề kỳ 2 - 新庭偶題其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A2n-v%C4%83n-h%E1%BB%8Dc-th%C3%ADch-H%E1%BB%93ng-C%C3%A1t-ch%C3%A2u/poem-HrYvDephDpfYnIZl-V2i2g">Tống Cố bát phân văn học thích Hồng Cát châu - 送顧八分文學適洪吉州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
